    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Oral statement to Parliament
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Statement on the Ockenden review of maternity services
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Patient Safety Minister Nadine Dorries gave a statement to the House of Commons about the Ockenden review of maternity services at Shrewsbury and Telford Hospital NHS Trust.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 10 December 2020
</div>

